lows rather than minimization of transport costs may be prioritized by the\nmicrovascular network.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Dec 2015 06:06:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Nov 2016 06:57:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 13 Jul 2018 02:19:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-16"}
