 We show that\n$(\\beta,A )$ allows preprocessing if and only if the spectrum $S_{{A}}(\\beta)$\nhas no accumulation point.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Dec 2015 09:45:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Feb 2017 09:45:22 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 18 Mar 2018 13:55:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-20"}
