 external quantum efficiency\nmodulation and power conversion efficiency enhancement in OPVs. Charge\ntransfers could also be used more broadly to tune the optical constants and\nelectric field distribution, as well as to reduce interfacial charge\nrecombinations within OPVs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Dec 2015 13:54:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 25 Feb 2016 05:49:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-26"}
